welcome_message_body: Welcome to Poinciana! Get ready to experience the charm of our vibrant city, known for its beautiful parks, friendly community, and diverse culture. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Poinciana has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A at Orlando International Airport primarily serves domestic flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Executive Terminal

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Private Aviation Terminal

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
